Sarri on Spygate: &quot;In Italy, yes [I've heard of it]. I don't know what to say. I prefer to study my opponents by video. It's very difficult to have a lot of information in the last two days [before a match]&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Sarri says he's never spied on opponents, adding: &quot;I'm not a very good spy, I think&quot;

